| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4542 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 407453a9-cd5d-594e-8343-9b0cc4d1d579"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
